Direct the Accountant to submit immediately all the 2018 accounts and financial reports to the Audit Team and henceforth, strictly comply with the timelines on the recording and submission of accounts to the Auditor, within the first ten (10) days of the ensuing month, as required by the abovementioned existing law, rules and regulations. Also look into the possibility of augmenting the Accountant’s Office of personnel from other departments, especially during report preparations and/or allowing them to render overtime, subject to availability of funds, in order to submit the accounts and financial reports on the mandated deadlines; 

